{"tid":1709731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰●天水圍】防暴警辱罵學生「唔讀書」","createTime":"2019-11-12T03:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T04:25:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd6d8a3e46a6cb07e5abf97057cbe821428e27d","tid":1709731,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:19:48.000Z","msg":"西鐵天水圍站連續第2日於繁忙時間停止服務。早上7時許，有市民於西鐵天水圍站往紅磡方向月台爭執，有人阻礙幕門關閉，列車無法駛離車站。有港鐵職員到場處理，但被市民包圍，要求解釋為何列車未能駛走，氣氛緊張。<br />\n接近早上8時，約30名防暴警員持盾牌進入月台範圍，有防暴警進入列車，帶走1名與在場市民爭執的中年男子，以及1名OL。<br />\n另外，有防暴警員於車站大堂截查3名穿校服的學生，查看他們的身份證，大罵他們「垃圾」、「唔讀書」。有市民欲行近拍攝，即被喝止「港鐵唔畀影相」，企圖阻礙拍攝。<br />\n現場有守護孩子成員進行觀察，有成員與防暴警員對罵。天水圍站其後宣布因特別事故而暫停服務，並呼籲市民盡快離開車站。<br />\n任文職的K先生向《蘋果》表示，自己欲往紅磡上班，對港鐵再次暫停服務感到不解，認為車站沒有受到破壞。「梗係唔合理啦，夜晚又早收，變相宵禁，佢哋喺為香港人服務㗎嘛，點可以話停就停呢？」。<br />\n由於港鐵暫停服務，導致巴士站人山人海，不少隊伍已「打蛇餅」，令K先生感到無所適從。對於網民發起三罷行動，他表示支持，認為現時的問題出自政府，「應該要問返政府佢想點」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191112/large/1573523337_b019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191112%2Flarge%2F1573523337_b019.jpg&h=922b6894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191112/60256837?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0L1QyApZ11f9Wce6VbxnL6Jr2aefMKt2-6OJAVoZ3MCMVE1JGgM1EJ1sw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60256837%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0L1QyApZ11f9Wce6VbxnL6Jr2aefMKt2-6OJAVoZ3MCMVE1JGgM1EJ1sw&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=e9237298\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60256837%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0L1QyApZ11f9Wce6VbxnL6Jr2aefMKt2-6OJAVoZ3MCMVE1JGgM1EJ1sw&h=096e4057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191112/60256837?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0L1QyApZ11f9Wce6VbxnL6Jr2aefMKt2-6OJAVoZ3MCMVE1JGgM1EJ1sw</a>"},{"pid":"1eb39c5651016a320d8d329129ee0e027c54c84f","tid":1709731,"uid":50457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:20:30.000Z","msg":"學生：防暴讀唔到書"},{"pid":"2598bdac95b05de6bf9dbc0e79c7e5d58f4b220b","tid":1709731,"uid":70745,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1eb39c5651016a320d8d329129ee0e027c54c84f","tid":1709731,"uid":50457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:20:30.000Z","msg":"學生：防暴讀唔到書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89888793172a512c4c98af275ec55b07e488bae5","tid":1709731,"uid":338276,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"好似自己有讀過書咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848da1c7bdd3374621855d047cd6f3087901c3e6","tid":1709731,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89888793172a512c4c98af275ec55b07e488bae5","tid":1709731,"uid":338276,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"好似自己有讀過書咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:26:08.000Z","msg":"就係讀唔成書先做黑警"},{"pid":"3840d82fa79fbf1ef91bed74662aab30d1dfff32","tid":1709731,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89888793172a512c4c98af275ec55b